<a name="newsitem970339283,91725,"></a>
<p><strong><font color="#f0f0f0">Blacksmithing Items</font> </strong><small>Posted Saturday, September 30, 2000 by <a href="mailto:jcsmith@gameznet.com">jcsmith</a></small><br>
This Saturday morning update includes a heaping helping of new blacksmithing items. It also features one new mob drop from Kithicor. I am eventually going to update the magic armor set section to include all of the new blacksmithing armor. I'm focusing first on getting caught up to date however so sit tight.<br><br>New 1HSlashs: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/scimitaroftheykesha.html">Scimitar of the Ykesha</a>(WAR).<br>New Piercers: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/seafarersharpoon.html">Seafarer's Harpoon</a>, <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/seafarersdirk.html">Seafarer's Dirk</a>.<br>New Breastplates: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/seafarersringmail.html">Seafarer's Ring Mail</a>.<br>New Leggings: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/seafarersringleggings.html">Seafarer's Ring Leggings</a>.<br>New Helmets: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/teirdaladamantitehelm.html">Teir`Dal Adamantite Helm</a>.<br>New Gloves: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/teirdaladamantitegauntlets.html">Teir`Dal Adamantite Gauntlets</a>.<br>New Boots: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/teirdaladamantiteboots.html">Teir`Dal Adamantite Boots</a>.<br>New Bracers: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/fieldplatebracer.html">Field Plate Bracer</a>.<br>New Cloaks: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/enchantedcabilisscalecape.html">Enchanted Cabilis Scale Cape</a>.<br>New Necklaces: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/seafarersringgorget.html">Seafarer's Ring Gorget</a>.<br>New Belts: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/enchantedcabilisscalebelt.html">Enchanted Cabilis Scale Belt</a>.
</p>
<a name="newsitem970284053,54479,"></a>
<p><strong><font color="#f0f0f0">More Goodies</font> </strong><small>Posted Friday, September 29, 2000 by <a href="mailto:jcsmith@gameznet.com">jcsmith</a></small><br>
Just a quick update before I head out for the night. Much of this equipment is being dropped form Loathesome Individuals. These individuals have replaced the rude invividuals in various zones(most notably Qeynos and Qeynos Hills). They are dropping some half way decent items. <br><br>In addition to the items posted below they also dropped various sword's such as the Initiate's, Apprentice etc Swords. I'm banking these are part of a quest some place as their stats are not that good in comparison. The casters are all dropping Damask Robes as well as occasionally dropping a 4 slot container book and words. I'm banking that you can combine the words that they drop into the book and get an item as a result. Thus far I have only been able to find 3 of the words however.<br><br>Anyway I need to head on out. Enjoy the items.<br><br>New 1HBlunts: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/runedbrandingiron.html">Runed Branding Iron</a>.<br>New 1HSlashs: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/befouledlongsword.html">Befouleed Long Sword</a>.<br>New Piercers: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/jaggeddiamonddagger.html">Jagged Diamond Dagger</a>(ROG).<br>New 2HBlunts: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/crostreewindsstaff.html">Cros Treewind's Staff</a>.<br>New Chestplates: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/ogrewarplatebreastplate.html">Ogre War Plate Breastplate</a>.<br>New Held Items: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/innoruuksword.html">Innoruuk's Word</a>(ENC).
</p>
<a name="newsitem970171144,86336,"></a>
<p><strong><font color="#f0f0f0">New Equipment</font> </strong><small>Posted Thursday, September 28, 2000 by <a href="mailto:jcsmith@gameznet.com">jcsmith</a></small><br>
Quite a few new items this morning. Three of these items are from a triggered spawn from one of the epic quests. A couple of others are intermediate rewards as well as a couple new smithing items and a few no drops from Kithicor Forest. Speaking of Kithicor Forest I realize that the zone guide is way out of date. If anyone would like to submit an up to date zone guide then feel free. If not I will be going through and updating it myself as soon as I get the chance.<br><br>New 1HSlashs: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/edgeofthenightwalker.html">Edge of the Nightwalker</a>, <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/runebladedswordofthenight.html">Runebladed Sword of the Night</a>.<br>New 1HBlunts: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/sceptreofixiblatfer.html">Scepter of Ixiblat Fer</a>, <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/imbuedogrewarmace.html">Imbued Ogre War Mace</a>.<br>New Piercers: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/cazicquill.html">Cazic Quill</a>(ROG).<br>New 2HSlashs: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/brassgoblinflamberge.html">Brass Goblin Flamberge</a>.<br>New Helms: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/circletoffire.html">Circlet of Fire</a>.<br>New Belts: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/ravenscalebelt.html">Ravenscale Belt</a>(ROG).<br>New Shoulders: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/mantleoffire.html">Mantle of Fire</a>.<br>New Necklaces: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/ogrewarplatecollar.html">Ogre War Plate Collar</a>.<br>New Masks: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/ogrewarplatevisor.html">Ogre War Plate Visor</a>.<br>Updated Magic Armor Set: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/ravenscalearmor.html">Ravenscale Armor</a>(ROG).
</p>
<a name="newsitem970101212,87261,"></a>
<p><strong><font color="#f0f0f0">Patch Date & New Servers</font> </strong><small>Posted Wednesday, September 27, 2000 by <a href="mailto:jsliski@icx.net">MiDWaY</a></small><br>
Well first of all there will be a patch on Thursday September 28, 2000 at 7:00 AM PDT.  Approximate downtime is 6 hours give or take a bit.  There are also 2 new servers coming up in the near future.  Tholuxe Paells is not a split server, it is for new characters only.  Drinal is split accepting log changes from Tunare and Mith Marr.  Log moving time will be on Friday, September 29, 2000 6:00 PM PDT.  Arrange this with your guild.  Remember wait a bit before issuing the /movelog command.  Thanks and keep checking for updates.
</p>
<a name="newsitem970077860,32796,"></a>
<p><strong><font color="#f0f0f0">Equipment Update</font> </strong><small>Posted Wednesday, September 27, 2000 by <a href="mailto:jcsmith@gameznet.com">jcsmith</a></small><br>
The equipment is slowing down a little now that many of the blacksmithing items have been posted and most classes are semi stumped in their epic quests. Here's a few items I had in the mailbox here on my laptop. I'll post some more up from home tommorrow.<br><br>New 2HBlunts: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/bluecrystalstaff.html">Blue Crystal Staff</a>(WIZ).<br>New 2HSlashs: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/imbuednorthmanbattleaxe.html">Imbued Northman Battle Axe</a>(WAR), <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/northmanbattleaxe.html">Northman Battle Axe</a>.<br>New Cloaks: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/ravenscalecloak.html">Ravenscale Cloak</a>(ROG).<br>New Neckguard: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/ravenscaleneckguard.html">Ravenscale Neckguard</a>(ROG).<br>Updated Magic Armor Sets: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/ravenscalearmor.html">Ravenscale Armor</a>(ROG).
