<p><strong><font color="#f0f0f0">Equipment Update</font> </strong><small>Posted Monday, September 25, 2000 by <a href="mailto:jcsmith@gameznet.com">jcsmith</a></small><br>
Today's equipment update consists of quite a few rewards for earlier stages of the epic quests. It appears that each classes quest will give a couple of these rewards along the way. These rewards may be somewhat random as well. <br><br>New 1HSlashs: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/trochilcsskean.html">Trochilc's Skean</a>.<br>New Robes: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/triumviratemissionaryrobe.html">Triumvirate Missionary Robe</a>.<br>New Shields: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/shieldoffalsehood.html">Shield of Falsehood</a>(SHM).<br>New Masks: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/ravenscalemask.html">Ravenscale Mask</a>(ROG).<br>New Shoulders: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/ravenscaleshoulderpads.html">Ravenscale Shoulderpads</a>(ROG).<br>New Earrings: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/twistedboneearring.html">Twisted Bone Earring</a>.<br>New Held Items: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/ballofeverlivinggolem.html">Ball of Everliving Golem</a>, <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/chaliceofkings.html">Chalice of Kings</a>(ENC).<br>Updated Piercers: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/ragebringer.html">Ragebringer</a>(ROG).<br>Updated Magic Armor Sets: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/ravenscalearmor.html">Ravenscale Armor</a>(ROG).
