<p><strong><font color="#f0f0f0">Rogue Quest Complete</font> </strong><small>Posted Sunday, September 24, 2000 by <a href="mailto:jcsmith@gameznet.com">jcsmith</a></small><br>
The highlight of tonight's update of course is the completion of the rogue epic quest. The result is Ragebringer a fantastic new piercing weapon. The rest of the update consists of primarily player forged equipment with one Plane of Sky quest reward. If you have submitted some information and it is not yet posted then please sit tight. I'm a bit backlogged. Had a busy weekend and i've been playing EQ a bit too much myself trying to figure the shadowknight quest out. =) I'll get to it all as soon as I can.<br><br>New 1HSlashs: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/antonianlongsword.html">Antonian Long Sword</a>, <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/koadadalfalchion.html">Koada`Dal Falchion</a>.<br>New 1HBlunts: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/theurgist.html">Theurgist</a>(CLR).<br>New Piercers: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/ragebringer.html">Ragebringer</a>(ROG).<br>New Chestplates: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/teirdaladamantitebreastplate.html">Teir`Dal Adamantite Breastplate</a>.<br>New Leggings: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/teirdaladamantitegreaves.html">Teir`Dal Adamantite Greaves</a>.<br>New Sleeves: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/enchantedcabilisscalesleeves.html">Enchanted Cabilis Scale Sleeves</a>, <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/teirdaladamantitesleeves.html">Teir`Dal Adamantite Sleeves</a>.<br>New Helms: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/enchantedcabilisscalecap.html">Enchanted Cabilis Scale Cap</a>.<br>New Bracers: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/teirdaladamantitebracer.html">Teir`Dal Adamantite Bracer</a>, <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/enchantedcabilisscalebracelet.html">Enchanted Cabilis Scale Bracelet</a>.<br>New Masks: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/enchantedcabilisscalemask.html">Enchanted Cabilis Scale Mask</a>.
